text: The shop officially opens at 7:30 AM, but Teresa consistently goes above and beyond, often starting to serve customers even earlier. Her coffee is always delicious and reliably consistent. I truly appreciate her exceptional service and dedication to crafting a great cup every time. The charming outdoor seating, with its quaint tables and chairs, creates a perfect spot to relax. Grabbing coffee from here has become an essential and cherished part of my morning routine.

Coffee here is very aromatic, delicious. If you buy a value card it's a really good deal too. I have breakfast at this outlet twice a week (they sell pastries too) and always enjoy talking to Teresa, the very friendly and cheerful barista! She makes an awesome cup of mocha :) It's a great start to the morning.

Cosy & casual seating outdoors, next to the entrance of Cold Storage.
You can get the coffee from their kiosk located right inside Cold Storage.
Tanamera Coffee has always been consistent, and you can get a good cuppa here.

Started frequenting this coffee shop during my maternity leave and soon became part of my routine. Teresa, the barista, is very friendly in addition to consistently brewing good coffee. I enjoy coming here almost daily. Thank you Teresa!

Teresa is the only reason Iâ€™m frequenting this coffee shop. Extremely friendly and always go above and beyond for her customers.

She deserves a big raise for keeping most if not all of your customers loyal to this shop.
